omnithreads version 0.1
====================

This module exposes interpreter threads to the Perl level.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module needs perl 5.8.0 or later compiled with 'useithreads'.

